KING Monada has asked the mother of his kids, Lerato Ramawela, to marry him. The musician has been with Lerato for more than 10 years and he has always referred to her as his wife. In this video clip, King Monada can be seen on one knee and presenting a ring to Lerato. He captioned the video clip: “If you tell me you love me, I might not believe you but if you show me you do, then I will.” The post saw his friends and followers congratulating them. ALSO READ : MASKANDI MBOKODOS RISE UP! Precious Mohale wrote: “She deserves it. She’s been with you through everything and supported you in everything you do. She’s a beautiful soul.” His friend Morwana Tshabakefete said: “Congratulations my guy. This is the dopest and smart move ever. This is the lady who has been there for you since day 1, osale DJ Monada, when we used to receive bad words from people calling us Makompo, when people used to bhooooo us while performing. She was there for you and supported you. I’m proud of you brother.” Cisky Miyelani Miye wrote: “Well done King Monada, congrats Lerato, you’re a strong woman. You’ve been through a lot. Wishing you the best in this journey.” 